FBIS3-52210 "drnes001_s_94025" FBIS-NES-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 Iran Condition Improves LD0301113894 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network in Persian 1030 GMT 3 Jan 94 LD0301113894 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network Language: Persian Article Type:BFN [Text] Ayatollah 'Abdolkarim Musavi-Ardebeli, the substitute Friday Imam of Tehran who has been hospitalized after suffering a stroke, is feeling better. In view of the improvement in his general condition, the medical team have expressed the hope that he will be released from hospital within the next few days.
